dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains the locations of warehouses in Kenya for 2012. Data were acquired from the World Food Programme. This layer is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. World Food Programme. (2012). Warehouses: Kenya, 2012. United Nations. Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/kz075fb6410
dc_publisher_s: United Nations. Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs
